  <brief_title>The Effect of Yoga and Laughter Yoga on Increasing the Psychological Resilience of Mothers</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Yoga and Laughter Yoga on Increasing the Psychological Resilience of Mothers With Their Babies in the Neonatal Intensive Care Unit</official_title>
